[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]how to protect public services and continue to reduce the deficit; 
[normal]4.2.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]how to ensure economic grow
[normal]th up and down the country; 
[normal]4.3.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]how to revitalise local democracy; and 
[normal]4.4.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]how to manage the contrasts between people’s experience of devolution in Scotland and Wales in the absence of an equivalent deal for England.
